Glacier:

- archival storage type
- check out & check in job will take several hours.
- should not be used as a backup solution
- 99.99 % durability
- SSL/TLS endpoint
- encryption at rest
- vault lock feature [ unable to change the content]

Data retrieval (price varies)
- expedited 1-5 mins
- standard 3-5 hours
- bulk 5-12 hours

We can setup lifecyle policies for glacier.
